tv-youtube-decline-worst-quarter-ever-subscribers-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay-TV%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20suffered%20its%20worst%20quarter%20ever%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%3A%20The%20next%20three%20months%20were%20not%20%3Cem%3Equite%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPay-TV%20distributors%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20conventional%20cable%20guys%20like%20Comcast%2C%20satellite%20TV%20outfits%20like%20DirecTV%2C%20and%20digital%20alternatives%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fyoutube-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20lost%201.6%20million%20subscribers%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20at%20MoffettNathanson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20very%20bad!%20But%20not%20as%20bad%20as%20other%20Q2s%2C%20like%20in%202023%2C%20when%20the%20industry%20lost%201.7%20million%20subscribers%2C%20or%20in%202022%2C%20when%20it%20lost%201.8%20million%20subs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20other%20good%20news%20for%20the%20TV%20industry%E2%80%A6%20well%2C%20that's%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%201.6%20million%20subscribers%20lost%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20account%20for%206.9%25%20of%20the%20industry's%20base%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20the%20slide%20is%20going%20to%20slow%20down%20at%20all%2C%20analysts%20Craig%20Moffett%20and%20Michael%20Nathanson%20write%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20no%20longer%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20floor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we've%20discussed%20here%20before%2C%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20there%20was%20a%20thought%20that%20digital%20pay-TV%20distributors%20like%20YouTube%20TV%20and%20Hulu%20Live%20would%20replace%20losses%20at%20conventional%20distributors%2C%20but%20that's%20no%20longer%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20those%20digital%20distributors%20are%20increasingly%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bseasonality%2