0tricky%20topic.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20in%20the%20early%20exchanges%20the%20AAP%20has%20demanded%2010%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20willing%20to%20give%20between%20five%20and%20seven%20only.%20The%20Congress%20is%20reportedly%20also%20willing%20to%20give%20one%20seat%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20of%20ex%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20KC%20Venugopal%20will%20likely%20meet%20Wednesday%20to%20sort%20this%20out%2C%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deadline%20for%20nominations%20is%20October%204%20with%20voting%20on%20October%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20word%20on%20this%20alliance%2C%20should%20it%20hold%20through%20the%20Haryana%20election%2C%20extending%20into%202025%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20election%2C%20in%20which%20the%20AAP%20has%20triumphed%20every%20time%20since%202013%20but%20faces%20a%20stern%20test%20this%20time%2C%20with%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20party%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20still%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20comes%20hours%20after%20it%20emerged%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20suggested%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20members%20continue%20the%20partnership%20formed%20before%20the%20April-June%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-election-congress-aap-rahul-gandhi-urges-party-to-consider-alliance-in-haryana-what-aap-says-6480753%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20Urges%20Congress%20To%20Consider%20AAP%20Deal%20In%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20wanted%20to%20retain%20the%20alliance%20to%20guard%20against%20division%20of%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024%20Haryana%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20contested%20the%20state's%2010%20seats%209%3A1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%20five%20from%20its%20share.%20The%20AAP%20lost%20the%20one%20seat%20it%20was%20contesting%20-%20Kurukshetra%20-%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Naveen%20Jindal%20by%20around%2029%2C000%20votes.%20The%20two%20parties%20got%2021.19%20per%20cent%20and%201.11%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20respectively.%20Combined%2C%20this%20was%20well%20below%20the%2036.5%20per%20cent%20amassed%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20Congress'%20vote%20share%20was%20lower%20than%20it%20managed%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20(in%20which%20the%20BJP%20got%20over%2058%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20votes)%20and%20Assembly%20elections%20(the%20BJP%20got%2036.49%20per%20cent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20consolidation%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20voter%20bases%20was%20seen%20as%20helping%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20win%20its%20five%20seats%20and%20stop%20the%20BJP%20from%20a%20second%20straight%20clean%20sweep%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similarly%20united%20showing%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20believes%2C%20is%20needed%20to%20vote%20out%20the%20state's%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20continue%20momentum%20generated%20by%20the%20party%20and%20INDIA%20bloc's%20strong%20showing%20in%20the%20general%20election%2C%20with%20statement%20performances%2C%20if%20not%20wins%2C%20in%20the%20four%20remaining%20state%20polls%20this%20year.%20The%20other%20three%20are%20Maharashtra%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-to-vote-in-3-phases-on-september-18-25-and-october-1-results-on-oct-4-6350146%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJ%26amp%3BK%20To%20Vote%20In%203%20Phases%2C%20First%20Assembly%20Polls%20Since%20Article%20370%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20the%20AAP%2C%20the%20party%20lost%20the%20one%20seat%20it%20contested%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20the%20Congress%20sees%20itself%20in%20a%20position%20of%20strength%20ahead%20of%20seat-sharing%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BFight%20Between%20BJP%2C%20Congress%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20tallies%20with%20what%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20this%20morning%20-%20the%20Congress'%20Haryana%20leadership%20responded%20tentatively%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20urging.%20Ex%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20members%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20apparently%20demurred%20giving%20up%20more%20than%20a%20handful%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20last%20week%20Mr%20Hooda%20seemed%20to%20play%20down%20the%20state-level%20import%20of%20the%20AAP-Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20partnership.%20%26quot%3BThe%20alliance%20we%20had%20was%20at%20the%20national%20level.%20We%20have%20not%20spoken%20to%20them%20(since).%20Here%20(in%20Haryana)%20the%20fight%20is%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%C2%A0Exclusive%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-election-bhupinder-hooda-exclusive-bhupinder-hooda-on-why-its-advantage-congress-in-haryana-polls-6421739%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBhupinder%20Hooda%20On%20Why%20It%20Is%20Advantage%20Congress%20In%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%2C%20for%20now%2C%20is%20maintaining%20a%20positive%20public%20face%3B%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20the%20party%20%26quot%3Bwelcomes%26quot%3B%20the%20alliance%20and%20stressed%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20priority%20is%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%20the%20AAP%20will%20contest%20Haryana's%2090%20seats%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20of%20its%20Central%20Election%20Committee%20on%20Monday%20(the%20CEC%20is%20the%20Congress'%20highest%20decision-making%20body)%2C%20the%20party%20apparently%20finalised%20names%20for%2049%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20may%20re-nominate%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20sitting%20MLAs.%20On%20the%20new%20faces%20shortlist%20are%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20Kumari%20Selja%20and%20Randeep%20Surjewala%20and%20a%20high-profile%20surprise%20-%20wrestler%20Vineet%20Phogat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725373920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-aap-alliance-in-haryana-negotiations-to-begin-soon-sources-6481958%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20have%20reached%20a%20'principal%20understanding'%20to%20ally%20ahead%20of%20next%20month's%20Haryana%20Assembly%20election%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Tuesday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Netflix's%20hunt%20for%20its%20next%20ads%20leader%20and%20what%20it%20signals%20about%20the%20company's%20future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gina%20Brogi%2C%20Amy%20Reinhard%20(R)%20at%20Variety's%20Entertainment%20and%20Technology%20Summit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d64