their%20relationships%20with%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20is%20conducting%20a%20wide%20search%20that%20includes%20people%20at%20rival%20tech%20and%20entertainment%20companies%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Roku%2C%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%2C%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20process%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20execs%20Netflix%20has%20recently%20targeted%20for%20at%20least%20exploratory%20conversations%20about%20sales%20roles%20there%20have%20deep%20digital%20sales%20experience%2C%20including%20Lisa%20Valentino%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdisney-ad-sales-executive-lisa-valentino-exits-restructuring-1236017671%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20Disney%20EVP%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20charge%20of%20some%20of%20its%20digital%20initiatives%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-ad-sales-chief-jon-steinlauf-top-execs-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWBD's%20Ryan%20Gould%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarner-bros-discovery-senior-ad-sales-exec-exits-layoffs-reorganization-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eex-WBD%20exec%20Jim%20Keller%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20with%20those%20credentials%20who%20some%20insiders%20think%20could%20be%20in%20the%20mix%20include%20Pooja%20Midha%2C%20EVP%20and%20GM%20for%20Effectv%2C%20the%20ad%20sales%20arm%20of%20Comcast's%20cable%20division.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20looking%20for%20someone%20who%20understands%20TV%20investments%2C%20linear%2C%20but%20has%20digital%20expertise%20to%20build%20products%20and%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20who'd%20had%20conversations%20with%20Netflix%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20really%20looking%20for%20a%20unicorn.%20And%20someone%20with%20sports%20experience%20is%20going%20to%20be%20important%20as%20they're%20making%20investment%20in%20sports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReinhard%20has%20been%20telling%20some%20people%20she%20wants%20a%20leader%20with%20a%20strong%20background%20in%20ad%20product%20and%20programmatic%20sales%2C%20which%20is%20increasingly%20the%20way%20advertisers%20want%20to%20buy%2C%20five%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20told%20BI.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20change%20from%20Naylor%2C%20who'd%20had%20leadership%20roles%20at%20Snap%20and%20Hulu%20and%20was%20best%20known%20for%20his%20deep%20relationships%20in%20the%20ads%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who'd%20had%20conversations%20with%20Netflix%20said%20Reinhard%20appeared%20to%20still%20be%20deliberating%20on%20topics%20like%20how%20much%20Netflix%20should%20rely%20on%20automated%20versus%20direct%20sales%2C%20how%20much%20the%20company%20should%20use%20outside%20partners%20to%20jump-start%20growth%20while%20it%20builds%20its%20own%20ad%20server%2C%20and%20how%20much%20it%20should%20share%20prized%20customer%20data%20like%20household%20income%20with%20advertisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20raided%20traditional%20TV%20companies%20and%20ad%20agencies%2C%20along%20with%20newer%20digital%20platforms%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-top-salespeople-advertising-team-jeremi-gorman-peter-naylor-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20its%20ads%20team%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20at%20its%20heart%2C%20Netflix%20is%20a%20tech%20company%2C%20and%20Reinhard's%20conversations%20have%20signaled%20to%20some%20that%20its%20center%20of%20gravity%20in%20the%20ads%20business%20is%20tech%20and%20product%2C%20not%20Madison%20Avenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20view%20ad%20sales%20as%20having%20a%20lack%20of%20rigor%20and%20discipline%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20person%20who'd%20had%20conversations%20with%20Netflix%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Naylor%20at%20Netflix's%202024%20upfront%20presentation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6699a44c49138fa6f6e3b41e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeter%20Naylor%20at%20Netflix's%202024%20upfront%20presentation.%3Cp%3EDimitrios%20Kambouris%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f84e46e-77f1-4290-bc21-8c03569d54ca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsiders%20say%20Netflix%20ads%20clashed%20with%20product%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20is%20by%20far%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-wins-streaming-wars-this-chart-shows-why-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edominant%20streamer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20278%20million%20subscribers%20worldwide%2C%20but%20it's%20looking%20to%20new%20areas%20like%20advertising%20and%20gaming%20(both%20under%20co-CEO%20Greg%20Peters)%20to%20keep%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20have%20said%20they%20expect%20advertising%20to%20eventually%20account%20for%2010%25%20of%20Netflix's%20revenue%2C%20but%20growth%20has%20been%20slow%20to%20materialize.%20Peters%20addressed%20the%20issue%20on%20the%20company's%20second-quarter%20earnings%20call%2C%20saying%20advertising%20revenue%20hadn't%20kept%20up%20with%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20ad-supported%20tier%2C%20and%20that%20the%20company%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20ahead%20to%20build%20all%20the%20features%20advertisers%20demanded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20task%20falls%20to%20Reinhard%2C%20a%20Netflix%20veteran%20and%20advertising%20outsider%20who%20was%20named%20ads%20president%20in%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsiders%20have%20said%20Netflix's%20adoption%20of%20ads%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-replaces-top-ad-ex-with-company-insider-surprise-shakeup-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efriction%20with%20the%20product%20side%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20on.%20They%20also%20said%20Naylor%20clashed%20with%20Jon%20Whitticom%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20product%20for%20advertising%20at%20Netflix%20under%20Reinhard%2C%20over%20which%20products%20to%20deliver%20for%20advertisers.%20Under%20Whitticom%2C%20Netflix%20enabled%20advertisers%20to%20buy%20its%20ads%20through%20tech%20companies%20like%20Google%2C%20The%20Trade%20Desk%2C%20and%20Magnite.%20It%20also%20plans%20to%20build%20its%20own%20in-house%20ad%20server%20to%20help%20advertisers%20leverage%20their%20buys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsiders%20said%20Whitticom%20was%20more%20focused%20on%20prioritizing%20programmatic%20tools%20that%20would%20help%20the%20company%20scale%20with%20advertisers%20of%20all%20sizes%20over%20features%20particularly%20important%20to%20Naylor's%20big%20advertiser%20clients%2C%20like%20certain%20geographic%20targeting%20abilities%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20keep%20their%20ads%20from%20appearing%20on%20content%20they%20deem%20unsuitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20insiders%20said%20Netflix%20also%20pushed%20back%20on%20giving%20advertisers%20access%20to%20certain%20information%20they%20rely%20on%20to%20validate%20the%20delivery%20of%20their%20ad%20campaigns%2C%20citing%20a%20desire%20to%20protect%20user%20privacy.%20It's%20possible%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20build%20those%20abilities%20itself%20and%20in%20a%20privacy-safe%20way%2C%20which%20would%20take%20more%20time.%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20have%20been%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20how%20they%20treat%20user%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix%20insider%20said%20these%20issues%20hampered%20the%20sales%20team%20in%20this%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstar-of-this-years-tv-upfronts-retailers-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETV%20upfronts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20entertainment%20companies%20make%20their%20pitches%20for%20the%20nearly%20%2470%20billion%20in%20annual%20TV%20ad%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sales%20team%20says%2C%20'You%20want%20to%20bring%20in%20these%20big%20numbers%2C%20you%20got%20to%20give%20us%20the%20tools%20advertisers%20demand%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20second%20person%20who'd%20had%20conversations%20with%20Netflix.%20To%20this%20person%2C%20Reinhard's%20keeping%20Whitticom%20was%20a%20sign%20that%20she%20valued%20product%20over%20salespeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsiders%20said%20the%20sales%20team%20also%20butted%20heads%20with%20the%20product%20side%20over%20how%20much%20of%20Netflix's%20highly%20coveted%20inventory%2C%20such%20as%20NFL%20games%2C%20should%20be%20sold%20programmatically%20rather%20than%20directly%2C%20where%20it%20could%20be%20sold%20as%20a%20centerpiece%20of%20larger%20ad%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Netflix%20spokesperson%20denied%20that%20Naylor%20and%20Whitticom%20clashed%20over%20product%20and%20said%20the%20company%20wasn't%20prioritizing%20certain%20advertisers%20over%20others%20with%20its%20programmatic%20rollout.%20The%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20company%20has%20allowed%20targeting%20by%20geography%20since%20the%20ad-supported%20plan%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20also%20said%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20proud%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20upfront%20results%20and%20pointed%20to%20an%20earlier%20announcement%20stating%20that%20it%20met%20its%20expectations%20and%20that%20sales%20were%20150%25%20higher%20than%20last%20year%2C%20without%20giving%20dollar%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22caaa6094-e98c-4416-8d8a-da8c54abcc12%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetflix%20had%20a%20slow%20start%20with%20advertisers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20embrace%20of%20ads%20after%20long%20eschewing%20the%20business%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20closely%20followed%20stories%20in%20advertising%20of%20late.%20It%20generated%20excitement%20among%20advertisers%20when%20it%20launched%20its%20ads%20tier%2C%20Basic%20with%20Ads%2C%20in%20late%202022.%20Advertisers%20were%20eager%20to%20appear%20near%20its%20prestige%20shows%2C%20and%20streaming%20ad%20inventory%20was%20scarce%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20effort%20got%20off%20to%20a%20rocky%20start.%20Some%20advertisers%20considered%20Netf