%3B...%20DGP%2C%20Manipur%20is%20requested%20to%20take%20all%20possible%20security%20measures%20for%20ensuring%20foolproof%20security%20for%20movement%20and%20transportation%20of%20new%20recruits%20of%2010%20IRB%2C%2011%20IRB%20and%20other%20personnel%20in%20their%20road%20journey...%20including%20safety%20from%20threats%20from%20above%2Foverhead%2C%20considering%20wide%20use%20of%20mortar%20bombs%20and%20drones%20as%20weapons%20by%20militants%20in%20the%20current%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Geoffrey%20said%20in%20the%20letter%2C%20which%20was%20also%20marked%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fr7ubgtno_manipur-generic_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20eventually%20announced%20it%20had%20cancelled%20the%20plan%20to%20send%20the%20recruits%20by%20road%2C%20which%20passes%20through%20narrow%20hilly%20roads%20where%20the%20convoy%20could%20be%20ambushed.%20Over%201%2C500%20IRB%20and%20other%20recruits%20were%20eventually%20airlifted%20to%20Assam%20from%20the%20airport%20in%20Manipur's%20capital%20Imphal%20on%20January%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20letter%20raising%20concerns%20over%20possible%20drone%20attacks%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%20asked%20the%20police%20chief%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20up%20necessary%20action%26quot%3B%20to%20install%20anti-drone%20systems%20at%20three%20important%20government%20buildings%20-%20the%20Governor's%20official%20residence%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Secretariat%2C%20and%20the%20assembly%20secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Reputed%20firms%2C%20capable%20of%20taking%20up%20this%20work%2C%20may%20be%20invited%20for%20presentation%20at%20an%20early%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20P%20Gojendro%20