0Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F1lqjs34_drone-manipur_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20month%2C%20a%20man%20who%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20sneak%20into%20Manipur%20carrying%2010%20high-end%20drone%20batteries%20for%20a%20terror%20group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-from-kangpokpi-carrying-10-high-end-drone-batteries-for-manipur-terror-group-arrested-by-assam-stf-5890838%5C%22%3Ewas%20also%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Assam%20STF.%20A%20filmmakers'%20association%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20however%2C%20had%20refuted%20the%20allegations%20against%20what%20it%20called%20a%20renowned%20member%20of%20the%20association%2C%20who%20simply%20bought%20the%20drone%20batteries%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20called%20the%20arrest%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20breakthrough%26quot%3B%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20use%20of%20beyond%20line-of-sight%2C%20military-grade%20drones%20by%20armed%20groups%20in%20Manipur%20amid%20the%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20scrambled%20its%20Rafale%20fighter%20jet%20to%20search%20for%20an%20unidentified%20flying%20object%2C%20suspected%20to%20be%20a%20large%20drone%2C%20that%20hovered%20near%20Imphal%20airport.%20The%20incident%20had%20delayed%20many%20commercials%20flights%20for%20over%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECivil%20Society%20Groups%20Ask%20Questions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECivil%20society%20organisations%20in%20Imphal%20valley%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fground-report-in-manipurs-foothill-village-koutruk-no-2nd-chance-to-rebuild-lives-after-suspected-kuki-insurgents-drone-attacks-6476530%5C%22%3Ehave%20raised%20tough%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20government%20over%20the%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20the%20government%20not%20trying%20to%20take%20this%20war-like%20situation%20seriously%3F%20Kuki%20militants%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20the%20state%2C%20so%20the%20question%20is%20what%20is%20the%20policy%20in%20national%20interest%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeetendra%20Ningomba%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Imphal-based%20Committee%20of%20Civil%20Societies%20Kangleipak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20Alliance%2C%20a%20global%20conglomerate%20of%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20while%20it%20appreciated%20the%20government%20and%20the%20police%20talking%20about%20taking%20measures%20to%20%26quot%3Bhold%20terrorists%20accountable%26quot%3B%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdisheartening%20and%20deeply%20worrying%20that%2070%2C000%20central%20military%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20deployed%20for%20counter-terrorism%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20protect%20lives%2C%20livelihood%20and%20properties%20from%20Kuki%20terrorists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fosaelehg_koutruk_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20Heritage%20Welfare%20Foundation%20in%20a%20statement%20called%20the%20drone%20attacks%20%26quot%3Ba%20clear%20act%20of%20terror%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20drones%20and%20sophisticated%20weapons%20previously%20unseen%20in%20this%20conflict%20demonstrates%20the%20militants'%20intent%20to%20inflict%20maximum%20harm%20and%20terrorise%20the%20Meitei%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20civil%20society%20group%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20latest%20Kuki%20m