20ideas%20for%20YouTubers.%3Cp%3ESpotter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESpotter's%20new%20AI%20studio%20scans%20a%20creator's%20YouTube%20library%20to%20give%20them%20video%20ideas.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20feature%20factors%20in%20previous%20video%20performance%20to%20help%20generate%20ideas%20that%20may%20drive%20more%20views.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESpotter's%20product%20lead%20says%20creators%20need%20more%20efficiency%20tools%20to%20compete%20as%20AI%20content%20spreads.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESpotter%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-softbank-backed-startups-spending-millions-old-youtube-videos-catalogs-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20creators%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%20as%20part%20of%20its%20catalog%20investment%20business.%20Now%2C%20it%20wants%20to%20offer%20them%20video%20ideas%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20it's%20launching%20a%20creative%20studio%20for%20YouTubers%20that%20uses%20generative%20AI%20to%20help%20them%20brainstorm%20video%20ideas%2C%20titles%2C%20concept%20art%2C%20and%20even%20different%20parts%20of%20a%20video's%20storyline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20trains%20on%20a%20creator's%20catalog%20in%20order%20to%20generate%20video%20ideas%20that%20match%20their%20style%20and%20tone%2C%20analyzing%20previous%20titles%20to%20imitate%20their%20typical%20structure.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20transcribes%20the%20audio%20of%20each%20video%20into%20log%20lines%20so%20its%20AI%20tool%20can%20understand%20how%20a%20creator's%20stories%20work%20so%20that%20it%20can%20pitch%20new%20ideas%20they%20might%20consider%20making.%20It%20does%20not%20analyze%20the%20visuals%20of%20a%20video%2C%20meaning%20it%20wouldn't%20pick%20up%20on%20non-audio%20elements.%20It%20looks%20at%20the%20performance%20of%20previous%20videos%20to%20identify%20top%20performers%2C%20what%20it%20describes%20as%20outliers%2C%20and%20recommend%20ideas%20that%20would%20do%20similarly%20well.%20It%20also%20scans%20the%20broader%20YouTube%20ecosystem%20for%20inspiration%2C%20mostly%20looking%20at%20video%20titles%20from%20related%20videos%20to%20come%20up%20with%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotter%20said%20it's%20been%20testing%20the%20feature%20in%20a%20beta%20program%20with%20creators%20like%20MrBeast%20(Jimmy%20Donaldson)%2C%20Dude%20Perfect%2C%20and%20Colin%20and%20Samir.%20The%20tool%20costs%20%2449%20a%20month%20and%20is%20available%20to%20YouTubers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20Do%20creators%20really%20need%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20help%20them%20come%20up%20with%20video%20ideas%3F%20Are%20creators%20feeling%20that%20uninspired%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Bakaus%2C%20Spotter's%20EVP%20of%20product%20and%20creator%20tools%2C%20thinks%20the%20company's%20studio%20feature%20will%20arm%20creators%20with%20an%20important%20tool%20to%20help%20them%20compete%20with%20a%20surge%20of%20AI%20content%20coming%20to%20YouTube%20and%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20much%20about%20helping%20creators%20come%20out%20on%20top%20in%20the%20wave%20of%20infinite%20AI%20content%20that's%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Bakaus%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20going%20to%20be%20so%20much%20generated%20AI%20video%2C%20both%20voice%20%5Band%5D%20audio%2C%20ideas%2C%20storylines%2C%20everything%2C%20that%20for%20humans%20to%20actually%20still%20come%20out%20on%20top%20will%20be%20infinitely%20more%20challenging.%20And%20so%20ironically%2C%20we%20are%20building%20software%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20have%20creators%20come%20out%20on%20top%20of%20that%20wave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraining%20AI%20models%20on%20YouTube%20content%20has%20become%20a%20touchy%20subject%20in%20recent%20months.%20Some%20of%20the%20biggest%20AI%20players%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F04%2F06%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-giants-harvest-data-artificial-intelligence.html%3F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-says-trained-on-youtube-videos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20transcribing%20YouTube%20videos%20en%20masse%20to%20generate%20training%20data.%20Spotter%20declined%20to%20share%20which%20base%20models%20its%20AI%20tool%20was%20built%20on%2C%20telling%20BI%20that%20it%20uses%20a%20series%20of%20commercial%20LLMs%20and%20diffusion%20models%20for%20various%20tasks.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20transcribes%20videos%20of%20its%20studio%20clients%20to%20recommend%20ideas%20to%20them%20individually%2C%20but%20not%20those%20of%20other%20creators%20on%20YouTube.%20It's%20taken%20measures%20to%20help%20ensure%20its%20content%20recommendations%20are%20unique%20and%20personalized%20to%20an%20individual%20creator%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20creator's%20responsibility%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20final%20videos%20are%20original%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20feature%20is%20meant%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20copilot%20for%20YouTubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20it%20has%20layers%20of%20content%20moderation%20for%20both%20its%20language%20and%20image%20generations%20to%20avoid%20producing%20content%20that%20pushes%20racial%20stereotypes%2C%20nudity%2C%20and%20other%20things%20it%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20show%20up%20in%20its%20studio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20of%20its%20creator%20studio%2C%20Spotter%20runs%20a%20business%20where%20it%20offers%20creators%20cash%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20licensing%20rights%20to%20their%20content.%20The%20company%20said%20it's%20paid%20out%20%24940%20million%20to%20creators.%20Several%20of%20Spotter's%20beta%20testers%20for%20its%20studio%20product%2C%20including%20MrBeast%20and%20Dude%20Perfect%2C%20have%20made%20capital%20deals%20with%20the%20company.%20Spotter%20also%20works%20with%20brands%20on%20advertising%20opportunities%20across%20its%20creator%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20new%20details.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotter-ai-helps-youtubers-like-mrbeast-with-video-ideas-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725372061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6008414a5cd1fcc8c7fb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotter-ai-helps-youtubers-like-mrbeast-with-video-ideas-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Creator%20startup%20Spotter%20is%20releasing%20a%20new%20studio%20tool%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20generate%20video%20ideas%20for%20YouTubers%20based%20on%20their%20own%20content.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dwhateley%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotter-ai-helps-youtubers-like-mrbeast-with-video-ideas-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Entod%20Pharmaceuticals%20gets%20DCGI%20approval%20for%20eye%20drops%20to%20treat%20presbyopia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725372003000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-06%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1685711759-6295.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fentod-pharmaceuticals-gets-dcgi-approval-for-eye-drops-to-treat-presbyopia-124090300633_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mumbai-based%20drugmaker%20has%20received%20a%20final%20approval%20for%20PresVu%20eye%20drops%20and%20plans%20to%20introduce%20it%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20October%22