20son%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bcow%20protector%26quot%3B%20but%20she%20has%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20chasing%20the%20car%20in%20which%20the%20student%20was%20killed.%20Maintaining%20that%20her%20son%20is%20innocent%2C%20she%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20the%20one%20who%20fired%20the%20bullet%20that%20killed%20the%20student%20and%20held%20up%20his%20work%20in%20%26quot%3Bcow%20protection%26quot%3B%20to%20illustrate%20his%20good%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20of%20evidence%20does%20not%20end%20there.%20NDTV%20went%20to%20the%20office%20of%20the%20main%20accused%2C%20where%20people%20said%20that%20he%20is%20well%20known%20as%20a%20cow%20vigilante%2C%20and%20also%20found%20YouTube%20videos%20posted%20by%20his%20organisation%20'Live%20for%20Nation'%20where%20its%20members%20are%20seen%20engaging%20in%20activities%20related%20to%20cow%20protection.%20Some%20videos%20also%20show%20cow%20vigilantes%20chasing%20people%20in%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMistaken%20Identity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2023%2C%20Aryan%20Mishra%2C%20a%20student%20from%20Faridabad%20was%20travelling%20in%20a%20Renault%20Duster%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20including%20two%20girls%2C%20when%20his%20car%20was%20chased%20by%20five%20men%20-%20Anil%20Kaushik%2C%20Varun%2C%20Krishna%2C%20Adesh%2C%20and%20Saurabh%20-%20who%20had%20mistaken%20them%20for%20cow%20smugglers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20tried%20to%20get%20the%20Duster%20to%20stop%20but%20Mishra%20and%20his%20friends%20chose%20to%20drive%20on%20because%20they%20thought%20goons%20had%20been%20sent%20after%20them.%20The%20men%20caught%20up%20with%20the%20Duster%20and%20opened%20fire%2C%20hitting%20Aryan%20twice%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20death.%20When%20the%20men%20saw%20the%20two%20girls%20in%20the%20car%2C%20they%20realised%20that%20they%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20and%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Kaushik%2C%20who%20is%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20and%20the%20four%20others%20were%20later%20arrested%20by%20the%20Faridabad%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20Cow%20Vigilantes%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Crime)%20Aman%20Yadav%20from%20the%20Faridabad%20Police%20said%20they%20have%20no%20evidence%20so%20far%20to%20indicate%20that%20Kaushik%20and%20the%20others%20are%20cow%20vigilantes%20or%20linked%20with%20any%20such%20organisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20visited%20Kaushik's%20house%20in%20Faridabad%20the%20same%20day%20and%20spoke%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20who%20gave%20details%20not%20only%20about%20his%20work%20in%20%26quot%3Bcow%20protection%26quot%3B%20but%20also%20the%20chase%20he%20was%20involved%20in%20on%20August%2023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20my%20son%20was%20chasing%20that%20car%20that%20night.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20cow%20smuggler%20in%20the%20car.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20first%20bullet%20was%20fired%20from%20the%20Duster.%20But%20he%20did%20not%20fire%20any%20bullets%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20whose%20bullet%20hit%20him%20(Aryan%20Mishra).%20My%20son%20is%20innocent.%20He%20protects%20cows%20and%20serves%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20saw%20two%20vehicles%20parked%20in%20the%20compound%20of%20Kaushik's%20home.%20The%20first%2C%20a%20Mahindra%20Bolero%2C%20had%20'Gau%20Raksha%20Dal'%20written%20on%20it%20while%20the%20second%20was%20a%20cow%20ambulance%20with%20the%20names%20of%20Kaushik%20and%20'Live%20for%20Nation'%20emblazoned%20on%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20address%20for%20the%20office%20of%20'Live%20for%20Nation'%20is%20Parvatiya%20Colony%20in%20Faridabad%20and%20when%20NDTV%20went%20there%2C%20it%20found%20the%20board%20outside%20said%20'Kaushik%20Properties'.%20People%20in%20the%20area%20around%20the%20office%20also%20said%20Kaushik%20is%20a%20cow%20vigilante%20and%20pointed%20t