usiness--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftoyo-india-to-do-feed-for-industrial-carbon-capture-project-for-eet-fuels-124090301073_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftoyo-india-to-do-feed-for-industrial-carbon-capture-project-for-eet-fuels-124090301073_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20New%20Law%20For%20Death%20Penalty%20In%20Rape%20Cases%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20massive%20protests%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%2C%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Assembly%20today%20passed%20the%20Aparajita%20Bill%20to%20amend%20some%20provisions%20in%20the%20criminal%20code%2C%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20for%20the%20state.%20These%20amendments%20make%20penalties%20for%20rape%20and%20child%20abuse%20more%20stringent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20Aparajita%20Bill%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bill%20seeks%20to%20amend%20several%20sections%20in%20the%20newly-introduced%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita.%20Section%2064%20in%20BNS%20lays%20down%20that%20a%20rape%20convict%20will%20face%20rigorous%20imprisonment%20not%20less%20than%2010%20years%20and%20this%20may%20extend%20to%20life%20term.%20The%20Bengal%20legislation%20tweaks%20this%20to%20enhance%20the%20jail%20term%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bremainder%20of%20that%20person's%20natural%20life%20and%20fine%2C%20or%20with%20death%26quot%3B.%20It%20also%20adds%20that%20this%20fine%20shall%20be%20fair%20and%20reasonable%20to%20meet%20medical%20expenses%20and%20rehabilitation%20costs%20of%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aparajita%20Bill%20also%20seeks%20to%20amend%20Section%2066%20of%20BNS%2C%20which%20lays%20down%20penalties%20for%20a%20convict%20if%20rape%20leads%20to%20the%20victim's%20death%20or%20causes%20her%20to%20be%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bvegetative%20state%26quot%3B.%20While%20the%20Centre%20legislation%20lays%20down%2020%20years%20jail%20term%2C%20life%20imprisonment%20and%20death%20for%20such%20a%20crime%2C%20the%20Bengal%20Bill%20says%20the%20convict%20should%20get%20only%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmending%20Section%2070%20of%20BNS%2C%20which%20deals%20with%20the%20penalty%20in%20gangrape%20cases%2C%20the%20Bengal%20legislation%20has%20done%20away%20with%20the%20option%20of%20a%2020-year%20jail%20term%20and%20laid%20down%20provisions%20of%20life%20term%20and%20death%20for%20those%20convicted%20of%20gangrape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20legislation%20also%20toughens%20the%20penalty%20in%20cases%20relating%20to%20publicising%20the%20identity%20of%20a%20victim%20of%20sexual%20violence.%20While%20the%20BNS%20has%20provision%20of%20jail%20term%20up%20to%20two%20years%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20Aparajita%20Bill%20provides%20for%20imprisonment%20between%20three%20and%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20legislation%20also%20toughens%20the%20punishments%20in%20child%20abuse%20cases%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20toughening%20penalties%2C%20the%20Bengal%20legislation%20includes%20provisions%20for%20setting%20up%20special%20courts%20to%20hear%20sexual%20violence%20cases%20and%20task%20forces%20to%20investigate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Comes%20Next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20moved%20by%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20cleared%20the%20Bengal%20House%20comfortably%20with%20the%20support%20of%20both%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20Opposition%2C%20but%20it%20will%20need%20both%20the%20Governor%20and%20the%20President's%20assent%20before%20it%20can%20come%20into%20force.%20Criminal%20Law%20comes%20in%20the%20concurrent%20list.%20This%20means%20that%20a%20law%20passed%20by%20a%20state%20Assembly%20can%20be%20implemented%20even%20if%20it%20is%20odds%20by%20a%20law%20passed%20by%20Parliament%2C%20provided%20it%20has%20the%20President's%20assent.%20But%20the%20President%20acts%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20ministers%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20Centre%20that%20will%20decide%20on%20whether%20this%20Bill%20becomes%20an%20Act.%20The%20Trinamool%20is%20a%20key%20rival%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20Aparajita%20Bill%20is%20unlikely%20to%20get%20a%20green%20signal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20had%20passed%20Bills%20mandating%20death%20penalty%20in%20rape%20and%20gangrape%20cases.%20None%20of%20them%20have%20got%20Presidential%20assent%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20Behind%20The%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Aparajita%20Bill%20is%20unlikely%20to%20get%20the%20President's%20go-ahead%20and%20its%20stringent%20provisions%20won't%20see%20the%20light%20of%20the%20day.%20Why%20then%20did%20her%20party%20push%20it%20through%20the%20Assembly%3F%20The%20answer%20to%20this%20is%20in%20massive%20outrage%20against%20her%20government%20over%20the%20August%209%20rape-murder%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20is%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20civil%20society%20over%20the%20heinous%20crime%20at%20the%20state-run%20hospital.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20on%20the%20main%20Opposition%20BJP%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20leadership%20has%20demanded%20a%20central%20law%20for%20death%20penalty%20in%20rape%20cases.%20This%20legislation%20appears%20to%20be%20another%20damage%20control%20exercise%20to%20manage%20the%20public%20perception%20and%20counter%20the%20criticism%20in%20the%20RG%20Kar%20rape-murder%20case%2C%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20her%20of%20shielding%20those%20responsible.