n%20Valley%20trip%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20tools%20boosted%20Headway's%20marketing%2C%20achieving%203.3%20billion%20ad%20impressions%20in%20early%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHeadway's%20AI-driven%20ads%20and%20features%20have%20significantly%20increased%20user%20engagement%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20weeks%20after%20OpenAI%20released%20ChatGPT%20to%20the%20public%20in%202022%2C%20Anton%20Pavlovsky%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20Ukrainian%20edtech%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmakeheadway.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeadway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20wary%20of%20the%20artificial-intelligence%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20his%20then-three-year-old%20company%20should%20adopt%20a%20defensive%20strategy%2C%20letting%20other%20companies%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20generative-AI%20investments%2C%20and%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20afterward%2C%20should%20they%20indeed%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20business%20trip%20to%20Silicon%20Valley%20the%20following%20April%20completely%20changed%20Pavlovsky's%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20talked%20with%20so%20many%20very%20smart%20people%20with%20lots%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20those%20people%20said%20that%20this%20is%20definitely%20a%20paradigm%20shift%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavlovsky%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20said%20that%20it's%20akin%20to%20the%20internet%2C%20the%20world%20wide%20web%2C%20then%20the%20smartphone%2C%20and%20then%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20return%2C%20he%20implemented%20a%20companywide%2C%20four-month%2C%20hardcore%20focus%20on%20AI.%20The%20company%20also%20created%20a%20separate%20cross-functional%20team%20to%20help%20integrate%20AI-powered%20features%20into%20its%20various%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPavlovsky%20said%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20has%20made%20a%20profound%20difference%20to%20the%20company's%20marketing%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%202024%2C%20the%20company%20said%20AI-driven%20ads%20reached%203.3%20billion%20impressions.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20had%20increased%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20from%20its%20video%20ads%20by%2040%25%20because%20it%20had%20helped%20lower%20the%20costs%20Headway%20would%20have%20previously%20spent%20on%20production.%20Headway%20declined%20to%20disclose%20its%20marketing%20budget%20but%20said%20it%20is%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmillions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20impact%20is%20on%20opportunity%20costs%20for%20people%2C%20it's%20freeing%20up%20so%20many%20resources%20on%20creative%20and%20more%20value-add%20endeavors%20for%20experimenting%20with%20crazy%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavlovsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeadway%20joins%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20marketers%20looking%20to%20harness%20AI%20tools%2C%20in%20part%20to%20reduce%20their%20advertising%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buy-now-pay-later%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-comments-ai-smaller-marketing-team-produce-more-savings-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKlarna%20made%20waves%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20it%20said%20AI%20had%20helped%20cut%20its%20spend%20on%20marketing%20agencies%20by%2025%25.%20A%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gartner.com%2Fen%2Fmarketing%2Ftopics%2Fai-in-marketing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGartner%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicted%20that%2030%25%20of%20outbound%20marketing%20messages%20from%20large%20companies%20would%20be%20synthetically%20generated%20by%202025.%20The%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20the%20tools%20has%20the%20marketing%20industry%20excited%20about%20AI's%20prospects%2C%20but%20some%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-is-set-to-dominate-cannes-lions-ad-festival-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euneasy%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20consequences%20for%20agency%20jobs%20and%20question%20%3Ca%