0challenge%20the%20best%20players%20in%20the%20world%20in%20such%20a%20state%3F%20I%20think%20I%20will%20have%20to%20accept%20it%20somewhere.%20Because%20two%20hours%20of%20training%20is%20not%20good%20enough%20to%20play%20with%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20players%20and%20get%20the%20desired%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENehwal%20said%20she%20is%20still%20considering%20the%20impact%20retirement%20will%20have%20on%20her%20but%20admitted%20that%20she%20would%20eventually%20have%20to%20take%20a%20call.%20The%20trailblazing%20star%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20BJP%20member%20now%2C%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20action%20more%20than%20a%20year%20ago%20in%20the%20Singapore%20Open%20where%20she%20lost%20in%20the%20opening%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20also%20thinking%20about%20it%20(retirement).%20It%20will%20be%20sad%20because%20it%20is%20like%20a%20job%20that%20a%20normal%20person%20does.%20Obviously%2C%20a%20sportsperson's%20career%20is%20always%20a%20short%20one.%20I%20started%20at%20the%20age%20of%209.%20I%20will%20be%2035%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20also%20had%20a%20long%20career%20and%20I%20am%20very%20proud%20of%20that.%20I%20have%20broken%20my%20body%20to%20a%20great%20extent.%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20what%20I%20have%20done%20and%20given%20it%20all.%20(I)%20will%20assess%20how%20I%20feel%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20said%20competing%20at%20the%20Olympics%20was%20her%20childhood%20dream%20and%20missing%20the%20showpiece%20for%20two%20consecutive%20editions%20has%20been%20hurtful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompeting%20at%20the%20Olympics%20is%20a%20childhood%20dream%20for%20all.%20You%20prepare%20to%20reach%20that%20level%20for%20years.%20Hence%2C%20at%20times%2C%20when%20you%20realise%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20make%20it%2C%20it%20hurts%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20exp