he%20time%20interval%20between%20the%20alarm%20and%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20deadly%20missiles%20was%20so%20short%20that%20it%20caught%20people%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20evacuating%20to%20the%20bomb%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukraine's%20Defence%20Ministry%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriting%20on%20social%20media%20website%20X%2C%20President%20Zelenskyy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20received%20preliminary%20reports%20on%20the%20Russian%20strike%20in%20Poltava.%20According%20to%20available%20information%2C%20two%20ballistic%20missiles%20hit%20the%20area.%20They%20targeted%20an%20educational%20institution%20and%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20partially%20destroying%20one%20of%20the%20telecommunications%20institute's%20buildings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20write%20that%20many%20are%20feared%20trapped%20in%20the%20debris.%20While%2041%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20more%20than%20180%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20are%20being%20carried%20out%20and%20several%20people%20have%20been%20rescued%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Zelenskyy%20also%20posted%20a%20video%20message%20for%20all%20Ukrainians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20received%20preliminary%20reports%20on%20the%20Russian%20strike%20in%20Poltava.%20According%20to%20available%20information%2C%20two%20ballistic%20missiles%20hit%20the%20area.%20They%20targeted%20an%20educational%20institution%20and%20a%20nearby%20hospital%2C%20partially%20destroying%20one%20of%20the%20telecommunications%20institute's%20buildings.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTNppPr1OwF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTNppPr1OwF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20%2F%20%D0%92%D0%BE%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BC%D0%B8%D1%80%20%D0%97%D0%B5%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D1%81