20by%20people%20so%20he%20is%20not%20popular.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20doing%20this%20before%20the%20elections%3F%20The%20lieutenant%20governor's%20post%20is%20an%20ornamental%20one.%20He%20is%20supposed%20to%20stay%20within%20his%20boundaries%20and%20work%2C%20but%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20before%20the%20elections%20to%20use%20his%20office%20for%20political%20reasons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20elections%20in%20Delhi%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20held%20before%20February%20next%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20has%20been%20no%20direct%20response%20from%20Mr%20Saxena%2C%20sources%20from%20his%20office%20rubbished%20Mr%20Bharadwaj's%20remarks%20and%20said%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20hiring%20an%20agency%20to%20handle%20the%20lieutenant%20governor's%20social%20media%20presence.%20They%20also%20reiterated%20that%20the%20AAP%20has%20allegedly%20spent%20Rs%203%2C000%20crore%20on%20advertising%20and%20asked%20how%20the%20party%20could%20even%20make%20a%20statement%20like%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20even%20know%20if%20the%20money%20spent%20by%20the%20party%20has%20come%20from%20foreign%20sources%20or%20taxpayers.%20What%20is%20wrong%20with%20what%20the%20lieutenant%20governor%20has%20done%3F%20We%20don't%20see%20anything%20wrong%20with%20it.%20The%20AAP%20is%20the%20last%20party%20that%20should%20talk%20about%20spending%20money%20on%20social%20media%20or%20advertising%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20showdown%20comes%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20the%20AAP%20had%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20a%20nearly%2030%25%20shortage%20of%20doctors%20and%20specialists%20at%20several%20hospitals%20in%20Delhi%20and%20accused%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Saxena%20of%20inaction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20had%20been%20made%20by%20Mr%20Bharadwaj%2C%20who%20holds%20the%20health%20portfolio%20among%20others%2C%20and%20the%20LG%20Secretariat%20h