%20on%20its%20'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fic-814-kandahar-hijack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIC-814%20Kandahar%20Hijack%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20web%20series%20to%20include%20hijackers'%20real%20and%20code%20names%2C%20Monika%20Shergill%2C%20the%20OTT%20giant's%20Vice%20President%20(Content%2C%20India)%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20benefit%20of%20audiences%20unfamiliar%20with%20the%201999%20hijacking%2C%20the%20opening%20disclaimer%20has%20been%20updated...%20code%20names%20in%20the%20series%20now%20reflect%20those%20used%20during%20the%20event%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Shergill%20also%20said%20Netflix%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20showcasing%20stories%20with%20authentic%20representation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20massive%20row%20had%20erupted%20over%20the%20Netflix%20drama%2C%20which%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20the%20hijack%20of%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20IC-814%20by%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen%20in%201999.%20Five%20hijackers%20took%20control%20of%20the%20plane%20and%20diverted%20it%20to%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20was%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Taliban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20released%20three%20terrorists%20-%20Masood%20Azhar%2C%20Ahmed%20Omar%20Saeed%20Sheikh%20and%20Mushtaq%20Zargar%20-%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20154%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Bhola'%2C%20'Shankar'%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20series%20was%20published%20hundreds%20of%20social%20media%20users%20accused%20the%20creators%20-%20Anubhav%20Sinha%20and%20Trishant%20Srivastava%20-%20of%20changing%20the%20names%20of%20two%20hijackers%20to%20'Bhola'%20and%20'Shankar'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20claimed%20as%20distortion%20of%20historical%20facts%20and%20critics%20have%20declared%20it%20misrepresents%20the%20terrorists'%20real%20identities.%20They%20have%20also%20claimed%20it%2C%20therefore%2C%20offends%20Hindu%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnobody-has-right-to-why-netflix-content-chief-was-summoned-over-ic-814-6473142%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20Has%20Right%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Why%20Netflix%20Content%20Chief%20Was%20Summoned%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20January%202000%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20had%20revealed%20the%20real%20names%20of%20the%20five%20hijackers%20-%20Ibrahim%20Athar%2C%20Shahid%20Akhtar%20Sayed%2C%20Sunny%20Ahmed%20Qazi%2C%20Mistri%20Zahoor%20Ibrahim%20and%20Shakir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20noted%20that%20during%20the%20hijacking%20and%20the%20hostage%20scenario%20they%20referred%20to%20each%20other%20by%20code%20names%2C%20two%20of%20which%20were%20'Bhola'%20and%20'Shankar'.%20The%20others%20were%20'chief'%2C%20'doctor'%2C%20and%20'burger'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalists%20who%20covered%20the%20hijacking%20live%20put%20out%20social%20media%20posts%20amid%20the%20controversy%2C%20saying%20that%20passengers%20had%20told%20them%20the%20hijackers%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20used%20these%20names%20to%20address%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPlaying%20With%20Indians%20Sentiments%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnetflix-indias-head-of-content-summoned-over-ic-814-web-series-row-6471163%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotests%20had%20led%20to%20Ms%20Shergill%20being%20summoned%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Union%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Ministry.%20Sources%20told%20NDTV%20she%20had%20been%20called%20as%20the%20government%20is%20taking%20the%20matter%20%26quot%3Bvery%20seriously%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20has%20the%20right%20to%20play%20with%20the%20Indian%20people's%20sentiments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontent-will-be-reviewed-sources-on-netflix-centre-meeting-on-ic-814-emergency-row-6479206%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BContent%20Per%20Nation's%20Sentiments%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre-Netflix%20IC%20814%20Series%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%20Netflix%20India%20officials%20met%20government%20officials%20for%20over%20an%20hour%2C%20after%20which%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20streaming%20service%20said%20future%20content%20will%20tally%20with%20those%20%26quot%3Bsentiments%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20social%20media%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20posted%20a%20vicious%20attack%20on%20X%2C%20accusing%20the%20creators%20of%20the%20series%20of%20trying%20to%20whitewash%20the%20criminal%20actions%20of%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20by%20giving%20them%20Hindu%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20like%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20criticised%20the%20selective%20outrage%2C%20and%20pointed%20to%20historical%20inaccuracies%20in%20other%20contentious%20films%20and%20series%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-surrounding-netflixs-ic-814-the-kandahar-hijack-6471958%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EControversy%20Surrounding%20Netflix's%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20political%20spat%20aside%20there%20were%20demands%20on%20social%20media%20to%20boycott%20Netflix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetflix's%20IC-814%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Netflix%20re-telling%20is%20inspired%20by%20eve