ent%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsmfg-india-credit-eyes-rs-60k-cr-aum-by-2024-25-to-focus-on-sustainability-124090300735_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsmfg-india-credit-eyes-rs-60k-cr-aum-by-2024-25-to-focus-on-sustainability-124090300735_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsmfg-india-credit-eyes-rs-60k-cr-aum-by-2024-25-to-focus-on-sustainability-124090300735_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Greats%20Tear%20Into%20Team%20After%20Embarrassing%200-2%20Defeat%20Against%20Bangladesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20cricket%20reached%20its%20lowest%20ebb%20on%20Tuesday%20while%20nosediving%20to%20a%20six-wicket%20defeat%20against%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20here%2C%20and%20the%20stalwarts%20termed%20the%200-2%20series%20defeat%20as%20%E2%80%9Churting.%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20Pakistan's%20sixth%20defeat%20in%20their%20last%2010%20Tests%20at%20home%20and%20this%20was%20also%20the%20first%20time%20Bangladesh%20have%20beaten%20their%20neighbours%20in%20a%20Test%20and%20series.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hurting%20that%20our%20cricket%20has%20come%20to%20this%20stage.%20Bangladesh%20deserve%20credit%20for%20their%20disciplined%20performances.%20But%20the%20way%20our%20batting%20has%20collapsed%20in%20this%20series%20is%20a%20bad%20sign%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20Test%20captain%20Javed%20Miandad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20Test%20saw%20the%20Bangladesh%20batters%20dominate%20the%20second%20innings%20after%20Pakistan%20dropped%20pacers%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20from%20the%20eleven%20and%20rested%20Naseem%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20had%20Bangladesh%20reeling%20on%2026%20for%206%20in%20their%20first%20innings%20before%20centurion%20Litton%20Das%20and%20Mehidy%20Hasan%20Miraz%20produced%20a%20spectacular%20partnership%20to%20rescue%20their%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiandad%20felt%20that%20the%20players%20have%20lost%20confidence%20because%20of%20the%20bickering%20in%20the%20Pakistan%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wouldn't%20just%20blame%20the%20players%20because%20whatever%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20board%20(PCB)%20in%20the%20last%20one%20and%20half%20years%20and%20the%20captaincy%20and%20management%20changes%20have%20affected%20the%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20captain%2C%20Inzamam-ul-Haq%20said%20losing%20three%20series%20and%20going%20without%20a%20win%20at%20home%20in%20nine%20Tests%20was%20a%20worrying%20record.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHome%20series%20were%20always%20considered%20our%20best%20chance%20of%20beating%20the%20best%20sides%20in%20the%20past.%20But%20for%20this%20to%20happen%20the%20batsmen%20need%20to%20get%20runs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20record-breaking%20batsman%20Younis%20Khan%20said%20when%20a%20team%20enters%20a%20losing%20streak%20mentally%20it%20becomes%20difficult%20to%20come%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20batters%20have%20got%20runs%20in%20the%20past%20but%20right%20now%20I%20think%20they%20need%20mental%20strengthening%20and%20a%20clear%20mind%20to%20overcome%20this%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Test%20batter%2C%20Ahmed%20Shezad%2C%20however%2C%20blasted%20the%20batters%20saying%20they%20hopped%20around%20against%20the%20Bangladesh%20pacers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20can't%20handle%20a%20bit%20of%20pace%20and%20movement%20even%20at%20home%20then%20the%20future%20is%20not%20very%20bright%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Test%20spinner%2C%20Iqbal%20Qasim%20asked%20the%20team%20management%20to%20groom%20existing%20and%20upcoming%20spinners%20as%20Pakistan's%20best%20chance%20of%20doing%20well%20at%20home%20was%20through%20spin%20bowlers%20and%20giving%20them%20helpful%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don't%20have%20bowlers%20of%20the%20calibre%20of%20Sarfaraz%20Nawaz%2C%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Waqar%20or%20Shoaib%20now.%20So%2C%20we%20should%20be%20banking%20on%20our%20spinners%20to%20win%20us%20Tests%20at%20home.%E2%80%9D%20Now%20with%20the%20latest%20setback%2C%20Pakistan's%20chances%20of%20even%20getting%20close%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20appears%20to%20have%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Shan%20Masood's%20lack%20of%20runs%20has%20added%20to%20his%20nightmarish%20run%20as%20the%20leader%20as%20he%20has%20now%20lost%20all%20five%20Tests%20at%20home%2C%20and%20he%20was%20not%20helped%20by%20the%20struggles%20of%20senior%20batter%20Babar%20Azam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20word%20is%20that%20red-ball%20coach%20Jason%20Gillispie%20and%20his%20white-ball%20counterpart%20Gary%20Kirsten%20have%20advised%20the%20PCB%20and%20selectors%20to%20not%20press%20the%20panic%20button%20as%20it%20will%20further%20dent%20the%20confidence%20of%20the%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Gillispie%20and%20high-performance%20coach%20Tim%20Nielsen%20will%20fly%20home%20to%20Australia%20for%20a%20short%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725360660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fuqscuk9o_babar-azam-afp_625x300_03_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-legends-tear-into-team-after-embarrassing-0-2-defeat-against-bangladesh-6480947%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20is%20hurting%20that%20our%20cricket%20has%20come%20to%20this%20stage.%20Bangladesh%20deserve%20credit%20for%20their%20disciplined%20performances.%20But%20the%20way%20our%20batting%20has%20collapsed%20in%20th