se%20India%E2%80%99s%20flag%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261493%2Favani-lekhara-gold-tokyo-paralympics-first-indian-woman-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20at%20the%20Paralympics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20he%20would%20fulfil%20his%20father%20Sunil%20Nagar%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20a%20sportsman%20who%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20continue%20his%20pursuit%20due%20to%20personal%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20made%20both%20his%20father%20and%20country%20proud%20when%20he%20won%20gold%20at%20the%20Tokyo%20Paralympics%2C%20becoming%20only%20the%20second%20Indian%20to%20achieve%20this%20in%20badminton.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Jaipur%2C%20Krishna%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20dwarfism%20at%20the%20age%20of%20two.%20Faced%20with%20the%20risks%20of%20treatment%20for%20his%20growth%20impairment%2C%20his%20father%20Sunil%20introduced%20him%20to%20various%20sports%2C%20unaware%20that%20this%20would%20become%20a%20game-changer%20for%20Krishna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Krishna%20played%20cricket%2C%20football%2C%20and%20volleyball%2C%20and%20even%20tried%20the%20long%20jump%2C%20believing%20that%20sports%20might%20help%20him%20grow%20taller.%20He%20shared%20that%20participating%20in%20athletics%20significantly%20improved%20his%20explosive%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESports%20became%20an%20escape%20for%20Krishna%2C%20providing%20refuge%20from%20the%20taunts%20and%20bullying%20he%20endured%20due%20to%20his%20height%20of%204%20feet%207%20inches.%20The%20bullying%20persisted%20into%20college%20and%20on%20the%20sports%20field%2C%20affecting%20him%20so%20deeply%20that%20he%20abandoned%20his%20favourite%20sports%20like%20cricket%20and%20volleyball%2C%20retreating%20into%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCsi7kFqtF6t%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3B