0see%20a%20lot%20of%20children%20engaged%20in%20odd%20jobs.%20Their%20conditions%20would%20remind%20me%20of%20my%20old%20days.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%20so%20that%20they%20come%20out%20of%20that%20circle%20and%20secure%20a%20brighter%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20faced%20opposition%20from%20his%20family%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20devote%20himself%20entirely%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20welfare%2C%20ultimately%20leading%20to%20him%20being%20kicked%20out%20of%20his%20home.%20Despite%20this%2C%20his%20determination%20remained%20unwavering%20as%20he%20continued%20to%20work%20tirelessly%20towards%20his%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComing%20from%20an%20underprivileged%20background%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20the%20children.%20I%20wondered%20if%20I%20could%20secure%20a%20government%20job%2C%20then%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20these%20kids%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20Amit%20started%20his%20first%20batch%20with%2010%20students%2C%20out%20of%20them%20six%20got%20government%20jobs%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20transformed%20their%20lives%20but%20also%20boosted%20my%20confidence%20as%20an%20educator.%20I%20started%20juggling%20between%20my%20job%20and%20teaching%20these%20kids.%20I%20also%20started%20devoting%20most%20of%20my%20salary%20to%20manage%20their%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20lifelong%20commitment%20to%20serving%20others%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20Amit%20has%20mentored%20350%20students%20to%20secure%20jobs%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20police%2C%20and%20Group%20B%20and%20C%20officers%20in%20various%20departments%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20has%20received%20constant%20support%20from%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20few%20fellow%20officers%20and%20old%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%2