Jalalabad%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20occurred%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20perfect%20these%20algorithms%20over%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20can%20eventually%20provide%20near-flawless%20support%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20technology%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20MARVEL%E2%80%99s%20work%20today%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20and%20human%20expertise%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fscience-and-technology%2F2024%2F07%2F31%2Fhow-america-built-an-ai-tool-to-predict-taliban-attacks%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98How%20America%20built%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20predict%20Taliban%20attacks%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20on%2031%20July%202024%2C%20Courtesy%20The%20Economist%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724680016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FIMG-20240826-WA0073-1724677884.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra%20government's%20MARVEL%20will%20augment%20law%20enforcement%20by%20developing%20AI%20tools%20to%20provide%20tailor-made%20solutions%20to%20the%20police%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362886%2Fmaharashtra-police-ai-tool-marvel-government-home-department-ips-officer-harssh-poddar%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Labor%20Prosecutors%20Challenge%20Amazon%E2%80%99s%20Claim%20It%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Employ%20Its%20Delivery%20Drivers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20company%20has%20